{"tid":368711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［公投］如果真係發生武裝起義，又會有幾多人參加？","createTime":"2017-08-21T17:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T15:07:34.000Z","uid":128007,"like":259,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"279854f6035f394dcc5791bbd52ebfe4f6d12822","tid":368711,"uid":128007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"前兩日遊行，眼見連登態度極不同，一方面話呢次遊行唔出黎，就係港豬，比人踩上心口都唔洗反坑<br />\n<br />\n另一邊又有人話，出黎遊行又只係行行企企，完全無用浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n咁如果家陣有一班武裝份子可以提供武器，協助你推翻港共，從回97拿前既香港，拎起武器，走上街頭去反抗呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死就死，點都要反抗架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要見血？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我都係番屋企啦"},{"pid":"cf1ed9bd57dd7a1ce537abe7148b46fe7ff00dff","tid":368711,"uid":83569,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"理想與現實，香港人真係唔敢。即使係旺角個班應該95%都唔會敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622d76bd79e58a8b926a5394bc25d9ec77b7d9da","tid":368711,"uid":128007,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理想與現實，香港人真係唔敢。即使係旺角個班應該95%都唔會敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩，如果你話唔受到傷既情況下，可以推翻到，我諗最少9成香港人都想，但係你話要打仗，我都係翻屋企算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df174dbc84be6ebb1d03509001e9a9372348a95","tid":368711,"uid":14476,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"你要知道你推翻嘅政權唔係香港政府，早啲瞓喇"},{"pid":"57beb18e58e3c8bc67eadc85209791de29d066ec","tid":368711,"uid":128007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要知道你推翻嘅政權唔係香港政府，早啲瞓喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係如果唔反抗，只會更明目張膽去侵蝕香港既主權<br />\n當時雨傘革命個期，就係中央挑戰我地底線過左火，搞到我地反抗，先安靜左排，家陣見香港人又唔理，就開始繼續溫水煮蛙"},{"pid":"80c624aac6c81b2e44a0dce3dbe1cfc3b2c3e44e","tid":368711,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"事成之後，可唔可以分番個督軍做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bbd02c5f46bbba205856ea1beb6b4d7b1afc9e","tid":368711,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事成之後，可唔可以分番個督軍做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申：講緊穿越去辛亥革命"},{"pid":"c04cf262dfff48b05957d901c6e404d60d78e358","tid":368711,"uid":128007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事成之後，可唔可以分番個督軍做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你係革命既帶頭者，先會有你份，如果你係後加入，你就可以成為專業既炮灰"},{"pid":"fb97f1775571051823269bee796347b62181bd80","tid":368711,"uid":128007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c796b8f34317ba8e6d090e25f8c674d83ca9129","tid":368711,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:17:09.000Z","msg":"你連登開post問有無人條j 50cm長都大把人答你有啦"},{"pid":"e3e54866986fd93a80ab9124eaa13ea7d0d2e178","tid":368711,"uid":137997,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"假如真係武裝起義到 比你運到武器入境 只會比籍口大陸放兵落來 唔洗兩日就血洗埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e8d8b821c1a59d0c662aa5052902a91e28dfb2","tid":368711,"uid":128007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假如真係武裝起義到 比你運到武器入境 只會比籍口大陸放兵落來 唔洗兩日就血洗埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假設係美帝同英國以違反中英聯合聲明以提供武器，同埋一d步隊駐港，不過極少量兵，只有大量武器，都時你會唔會為自己未來出力？"},{"pid":"256f059c943667b0f3b7633fd3da9b61d8135383","tid":368711,"uid":54424,"li